# Diagnostic: kick on every quarter, hi-hat on every 8th. No snare.
# Should sound like a metronome with a tick-tock between each kick.
# If this feels tight but the full four-on-the-floor doesn't, the
# problem is the snare interaction, not timing.

bpm: 120
steps: 16

kick:  x---x---x---x---
hihat: x-x-x-x-x-x-x-x-
